PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works of certain persons as directors of the board of directors of Harbourfront Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (W. Darcy McKeough, Toronto, Ontario, in the place of Gordon Joseph Chong, whose term has expired; and Brian J. Veinot, Gloucester, Ontario, in the place of Ray Biggart, who has resigned)
